    {
      "id": "owasp",
      "label": "OWASP",
      "icon": "🛡️",
      "title_prefix": "OWASP",
      "default_tags": [
        "web",
        "owasp"
      ],
      "variants": [
        {
          "id": "top-ten",
          "label": "General Web",
          "title_prefix": "OWASP Top 10 Web Checklist",
          "body_lines": [
            "## 🧪 OWASP Top 10 + WSTG Deep Dive",
            "",
            "- **TARGET:** <DOMAIN>/",
            "",
            "### 🛡️ A01: Broken Access Control [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **IDOR Check:** Change `user_id` or `UUID` in URLs/JSON. Try numeric increment/decrement.",
            "- [ ] **CORS Misconfig:** Check for `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *` or `null`. Check for origin reflection.",
            "- [ ] **Method Bypass:** Try `PUT` or `DELETE` on endpoints that only show `GET/POST`.",
            "- **Remediation:** Implement object-level authorization and strict CORS whitelisting.",
            "",
            "### 🔐 A02: Cryptographic Failures [Severity: High/Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Sensitive Data in URL:** Check for tokens/PII in GET parameters (browser history leak).",
            "- [ ] **Weak TLS:** Use `testssl.sh`. Check for TLS 1.0/1.1 or Null Ciphers.",
            "- [ ] **Secure Cookies:** Verify `HttpOnly`, `Secure`, and `SameSite` flags.",
            "- **Remediation:** Use TLS 1.2+ and encrypt PII at rest/transit.",
            "",
            "### 💉 A03: Injection [Severity: High/Critical]",
            "- [ ] **SQLi:** Try `'`, `\"`, `1' OR 1=1--`, and Time-based payloads.",
            "- [ ] **XSS:** Test `<script>alert(1)</script>` and DOM-based sinks.",
            "- [ ] **SSTI:** Try `{{7*7}}` or `${7*7}` in template-heavy apps.",
            "- **Remediation:** Use parameterized queries and context-aware output encoding.",
            "",
            "### 🎨 A04: Insecure Design [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Logic Bypass:** Can you skip a payment/auth step via direct URL access?",
            "- [ ] **Race Conditions:** Send 20+ concurrent requests for state-changing actions.",
            "- **Remediation:** Enforce server-side state machine logic.",
            "",
            "### ⚙️ A05: Security Misconfiguration [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Default Creds:** Check for `admin:admin`, `guest:guest`, etc.",
            "- [ ] **Verbose Errors:** Trigger a 500 error; look for stack traces or DB versions.",
            "- [ ] **Cloud Metadata:** Check for `http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/` via SSRF/LFI.",
            "- **Remediation:** Harden headers and disable directory indexing/verbose errors.",
            "",
            "### 📦 A06: Vulnerable Components [Severity: Medium/High]",
            "- [ ] **Header Inspection:** Check `X-Powered-By` for outdated versions.",
            "- [ ] **Dependency Confusion:** Check internal repo names vs public registries.",
            "- **Remediation:** Establish a patch management cycle for all 3rd party libs.",
            "",
            "### 👤 A07: Auth Failures [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **Brute Force:** Check for lack of account lockout or rate limiting.",
            "- [ ] **MFA Bypass:** Can you browse to `/dashboard` while MFA is active?",
            "- **Remediation:** Enforce MFA and rate-limit authentication endpoints.",
            "",
            "### 🧩 A08: Data Integrity [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **JWT Analysis:** Check for `\"alg\": \"none\"` or RS256-to-HS256 key confusion.",
            "- [ ] **Deserialization:** Look for base64 serialized objects in cookies (Java/PHP).",
            "- **Remediation:** Digitally sign all serialized data; use safe parsers.",
            "",
            "### 📊 A09: Logging/Monitoring [Severity: Low]",
            "- [ ] **Log Injection:** Use `\\n` in a username to forge log entries.",
            "- **Remediation:** Sanitize all data written to logs.",
            "",
            "### 🌐 A10: SSRF [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **Internal Scan:** Try `http://localhost:22` or `http://127.0.0.1:80`.",
            "- [ ] **OOB Interaction:** Use Burp Collaborator to detect blind SSRF.",
            "- **Remediation:** Use a whitelist for outbound requests; isolate the network.",
            "",
            "---",
            "## 📝 Findings & PoC",
            "| ID | Impact | Status |",
            "|----|--------|--------|",
            "|    |        |        |",
            "",
            "**Payload:** `code here`"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "api",
          "label": "API Specific",
          "title_prefix": "OWASP API Security",
          "body_lines": [
            "## 🔌 OWASP API Security Top 10",
            "",
            "- **TARGET:** <DOMAIN>/",
            "",
            "### 🔑 API1: BOLA (IDOR) [Severity: High/Critical]",
            "- [ ] **ID Substitution:** Access `/api/v1/messages/{id}` of another user.",
            "- **Remediation:** Check authorization for every object access request.",
            "",
            "### 🆔 API2: Broken Authentication [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **Token Expiry:** Do JWTs/API keys expire? Are they revoked on logout?",
            "- **Remediation:** Use standard OIDC/OAuth; enforce short token lifespans.",
            "",
            "### 📤 API3: Object Property Level Auth [Severity: Medium/High]",
            "- [ ] **Mass Assignment:** Can you add `\"is_admin\": true` to profile JSON?",
            "- [ ] **Excessive Exposure:** Does the API return full user objects (hashes/PII)?",
            "- **Remediation:** Use DTOs to filter input/output properties.",
            "",
            "### 📉 API4: Unrestricted Resource Consumption [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Rate Limiting:** Send 1k requests/min. Check for 429 errors.",
            "- [ ] **Pagination Stress:** Try `?limit=999999` to cause memory exhaustion.",
            "- **Remediation:** Implement per-user/per-IP rate limits and max page sizes.",
            "",
            "### 🧱 API5: Broken Function Level Auth [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **Admin Method:** Try `DELETE` on a resource as a standard user.",
            "- **Remediation:** Centralize authorization checks for admin functions.",
            "",
            "### 🗺️ API6: Business Logic [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Step Skipping:** Move to 'Shipment' without 'Payment' via API calls.",
            "- **Remediation:** Validate business workflow states on the server.",
            "",
            "### 🛰️ API7: SSRF [Severity: High]",
            "- [ ] **Webhooks:** Point callback URLs to internal IP space.",
            "- **Remediation:** Validate callback URLs against a strict allowlist.",
            "",
            "### ⚙️ API8: Security Misconfiguration [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Method Enforcement:** Does the API reject `DEBUG`, `TRACE`, or `HEAD`?",
            "- [ ] **GraphQL:** Is `__schema` introspection enabled?",
            "- **Remediation:** Disable unnecessary methods and GraphQL introspection in production.",
            "",
            "### 📦 API9: Inventory Management [Severity: Low/Medium]",
            "- [ ] **Shadow APIs:** Fuzz for `/api/v1/`, `/api/dev/`, `/api/test/`.",
            "- **Remediation:** Maintain a current API registry and sunset old versions.",
            "",
            "### 🌪️ API10: Unsafe Consumption [Severity: Medium]",
            "- [ ] **3rd Party Trust:** Sanitize data from integrated APIs (Stripe/AWS/etc).",
            "- **Remediation:** Treat all integrated data as untrusted input.",
            "",
            "---",
            "## 📝 API Findings Table",
            "| Endpoint | Method | Risk | Status |",
            "|----------|--------|------|--------|",
            "|          |        |      |        |"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "body_lines": [
        "## OWASP Assessment",
        ""
      ]
